data.name: textBoxDescription.Text
data.value: Tiotag Database (R) was designed for ICS4U final at Stratford Central Secondary School in Stratford, Ontario, Canada. Use this program to create your own custom database in the TIOTAG (*.tiotag) file format [an altered version of an XML (*xml) file]. The TIOTAG file format is executable by this program as well as most programs that are able to execute XML file formats. Please report any bugs to gibsonmacmillan@outlook.com.
